# Personal data — your candidate inputs (keep your own privately)
# profile/  — un-comment if YOU want to keep your profile private
#             (default: ship it as an example; remove for the public repo)

# State / sessions are stored outside the repo (~/.job_search/) so no .gitignore entry needed

# /apply personal data — real answers file has your address, phone, GPA, EEO answers
# (the .example.json file IS committed as the schema template)
scripts/answers.json
answers.json

# Cover-letter templates — commit README.md but not personal templates
scripts/covers/default.md
scripts/covers/*.md
!scripts/covers/README.md

